FT  31 DEC 92 / World News in Brief: Dial 112 for help
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
An emergency telephone number covering much of Europe comes into effect
tomorrow. Except in Spain and the Netherlands, dialling 112 in an EC country
will link you to the local police, fire or ambulance. The UK service will be
in addition to the 999 operation.
