FT  29 DEC 92 / World Stock Markets: South Africa
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
GAINS in industrial and financial shares lifted Johannesburg as the
all-share index rose 10 to 3,256. The industrial index added 18 to 4,356
while the gold index shed 1 to 816.
Last Thursday, industrials rose 10 to 4,338 and the all-share index was 5 up
at 3,246. Golds were steady at 817.
