also convert some debt into a maximum of Pounds 10.6m in loan notes, in
addition to providing further credit facilities.
Pre-tax losses fell from Pounds 7.43m to Pounds 4m in the half year to
September 30. Turnover amounted to Pounds 4.49m (Pounds 6.86m).
